              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "Layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EDidn\u2019t find what you\u2019re looking for? The Service Portal is available to all @nebraska.gov users and is located at \u003Ca target=\u0022_blank\u0022 data-router-slot=\u0022disabled\u0022 href=\u0022https://serviceportal.ne.gov\u0022 title=\u0022https://serviceportal.ne.gov\u0022 type=\u0022external\u0022\u003Ehttps://serviceportal.ne.gov\u003C/a\u003E, or call us directly at \u003Cstrong\u003E402.471.4636\u003C/strong\u003E or \u003Cstrong\u003E800.982.2468\u003C/strong\u003E. Our phones are answered at all times, 3:00PM or 3:00AM by State of Nebraska employees located right here in Lincoln, Nebraska.\u003C/p\u003E"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
